title: Week 2 review
itunes:title: Week 2 review
description:
A room filled with heroes - Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling, Marc Sessler and Colleen Wolfe – recap all the games from the second week of the regular season including the injury-riddled Cowboys defeating the Eagles and the Seahawks falling to 0-2. Plus, each hero shares his biggest takeaway from Week 2 of the 2015 season.
